'''轉化糖漿'''是一種由[[葡萄糖|葡萄糖]]和[[果糖|果糖]]合成的黃褐色混合物，而上述兩類糖份是通過[[蔗糖|蔗糖]]在水中加熱而取得。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sugar.org/consumers/sweet_by_nature.asp?id=275 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090301033842/http://www.sugar.org/consumers/sweet_by_nature.asp?id=275 |archive-date=2009-03-01 |publisher=The Sugar Association |title=What are the types of sugar? |deadurl=yes }}</ref>轉化糖漿的[[甜度|甜度]]較蔗糖高<ref>{{cite web |title = Making simple syrup is an exercise in chemical reactions |work = A Word from Carol Kroskey |url = http://www.bakers-exchange.com/articles/2000/april.html |accessdate = 2006-05-01 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070714004114/http://www.bakers-exchange.com/articles/2000/april.html |archivedate = 2007-07-14 |quote = In addition to increased moisture retention ability, converting sucrose to invert syrup has two other interesting results: increased sweetness and better solubility. On a sweetness scale where sucrose is set at 100, invert syrup ranks about 130. }}</ref>，且可保持較多水份及不易[[結晶|結晶]]，由於這些特質，轉化糖漿的產品在[[烘焙|烘焙]]作業中備受推崇。<ref>{{Cite book |first1 = Hubert |last1 = Schiweck |first2 = Margaret |last2= Clarke |first3 = Günter |last3 = Pollack |chapter = Sugar |title = Ullmann’s Encyclopedia of Industrial Chemistry |year = 2007 |publisher = Wiley-VCH |location = Weinheim |doi = 10.1002/14356007.a25_345.pub2 }}</ref>

蔗糖的分子結構是屬由兩個[[單醣|單醣]]組合而成的[[雙醣|雙醣]]，通過加熱含蔗糖的溶液，使蔗糖產生[[水解反應|水解反應]]，進而分解成屬於單醣的果糖和葡萄糖，這種糖漿的旋光度與普通的糖相反，所以稱爲“轉化糖漿”。上述的水解反應通常可藉著添加[[催化劑|催化劑]]而加快，這些催化劑包括蔗糖酶及轉化糖苷水解酶，另使用含有[[果酸|果酸]]成份的物質如檸檬汁也可加快轉化過程。

